{"tid":1860130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「好淆，但罷！」","createTime":"2020-02-03T13:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T13:45:28.000Z","uid":298704,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f0aadb7efbe419188910c2a51cc9f880e0100c94","tid":1860130,"uid":298704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:20:04.000Z","msg":"屋企人系前線緊急醫護<br />\n系瑪格烈傳染病中心(IDC) 做<br />\n感多日黎睇緊好多確診Case<br />\n每次番屋企都好攰好嬲<br />\n嬲啲中國人態度差嬲個政府感仆街<br />\n驚帶啲菌比我地<br />\n今日第一階段罷工<br />\n今日膠層逐個見威迫利誘施壓佢地<br />\n佢地真系好驚俾人秋後算帳<br />\n好驚以後被人炒冇得再做醫護<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em><em><ins><span style=\"color: pink;\">「好淆，但罷！齊上齊落！」</span></ins></em></em></span></span></strong><br />\n佢系個Ward 既group覆<br />\n醫護第二階段罷工<br />\n正 式 開 始<br />\n<br />\n好撚為有呢個屋企人自豪<br />\n香港人 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">加入工會 三罷救港</span></span></strong><br />\n你入左工會 準備好同醫護一齊罷未 <br />\n負好守護香港 守護身邊人既責任未？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8iS8qQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8iS8qQ.jpg&h=f9c4b278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dybtGLR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdybtGLR.jpg&h=24ff0911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UdMEOqR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUdMEOqR.jpg&h=aee5dd53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rTtscSx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrTtscSx.jpg&h=d9ba584b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJ5urcy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJ5urcy.jpg&h=4a5a0f90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dec295c1dc353971407cac3fdd4843aa381c3ec2","tid":1860130,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:26:02.000Z","m